0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:27:49.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑"},{"pid":"67fa3baccb9c5d6adbadd71914dded53512491d0","tid":1636673,"uid":26041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:30:04.000Z","msg":"文宣新方法！ 以連豬做四格漫畫！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1635818\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1635818</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見到south park 咁大回響，就發現文宣最緊要易入口，好似 Joan Cornella咁，將每人發生既事記錄落黎，大家睇幾秒就明曬，而且又容易翻譯做唔同語言。而且漫畫容易引人追睇，易入屋又易收藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經係手足可以幫手畫畫，如果連登仔一齊諗橋，其實一日兩三篇絕對唔難，又可以支援國際戰線，又可以吸引多d人睇！<br />\n<br />\n大家可以幫手諗埋角色設定：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連豬： 深黃勇武派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連狗： 和理非<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />腦魔： 記者？<br />\n<br />\n其實一開始可以畫d易入口d, 好似老夫子咁深入淺出容易吸引d深黃淺藍 （深黃跟本唔洗睇佢都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），又容易translate做其他語言，例如：<br />\n<br />\n1.為所欲為Tee ( 講腦魔教連狗著為所欲為tee，然後比連豬整蠱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 連豬病都冇得帶口罩，變咗豬流感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.或者用連豬連狗將一d好人好事，黃絲小店分享比大家，例如全民幫黃店清潔同say sorry（或者講下咩店唔幫襯得）<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213abd902b33c782424504b4dc6bb38f576dc253","tid":1636673,"uid":42182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"靚抽<br />\n如果south park 有集講香港就好囉"},{"pid":"5d819586de51758d3ce71f2ae7f8b6a7c7904183","tid":1636673,"uid":222803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:54:24.000Z","msg":"Please use English or other language instead of Cantonese to spread the information<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae71f54fbb395029cded8def88da2b6e483a048c","tid":1636673,"uid":51698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"其實係south park發咗聲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}